    <h3>Types of Smart Locks</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-3 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Retrofit Locks</h4>
            <p>Install on your existing deadbolt without changing the exterior appearance.</p>
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Renters, minimal installation
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Full Replacement</h4>
            <p>Complete deadbolt replacement with integrated smart features.</p>
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Homeowners wanting full smart integration
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Smart Handles</h4>
            <p>Replace entire door handle and lock mechanism.</p>
            <strong>Best for:</strong> New construction or major renovations
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3>Unlock Methods</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-2 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Keypad Entry</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Enter numeric codes to unlock</li>
