                <li>Temporary codes for visitors</li>
                <li>No smartphone required</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>App Control</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Unlock from anywhere with internet</li>
                <li>Monitor lock activity and history</li>
                <li>Share digital keys with others</li>
                <li>Integration with smart home systems</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3>Installation Considerations</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Door Compatibility:</strong> Check door thickness and deadbolt requirements</li>
        <li><strong>Power Source:</strong> Most use batteries, consider battery life</li>
        <li><strong>Connectivity:</strong> WiFi, Bluetooth, or hub-required models</li>
        <li><strong>Security Features:</strong> Encryption, auto-lock, tamper alerts</li>
        <li><strong>Weather Resistance:</strong> Important for exterior doors</li>
        <li><strong>Backup Access:</strong> Physical key or alternative entry method</li>
    </ul>
</section>

